FBIS3-53029 "drnes007_n_94003" FBIS-NES-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 LEBANON U.S. Firms Said Encouraged To Buy Land in South NC1101072894 Beirut AL-'AHD in Arabic 31 Dec 93 p 9 NC1101072894 Beirut AL-'AHD Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Informed sources have stated that the U.S. Embassy is encouraging U.S. firms and businessmen to buy land in the "occupied strip" [Israel's self-declared security zone in south Lebanon]. This information coincides with reports from Marj 'Uyun that a U.S. company has bought vast tracts of lands in Sarda and al-'Umrah near the al-Wazzani water spring.
